narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments:
I appreciate that the course tried to be hands-on, because the best way to learn is by doing in this scenario. 

However, I don't know that the format of content presentation lent itself well to a seminar style. Things ultimately were a bit jumbled, and without a passion for the subject of our projects, it was hard to engage.
the material was very repetitive from class to class
